{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he stayed with us for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- actually, it was not a very good place to hide because we were [INAUDIBLE] by ourself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nevertheless, one day when they finally-- somebody must have squealed on him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we finally found-- when they finally came to our place he-- he managed to evade them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He jumped through the window, and then changed his clothes and-- and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I say, that was when the Russians-- when we still lived in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And only later, in Dubno, I-- I heard that he's a police chief.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lwow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was one of the things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were other people from Rowne who live in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow my mother felt-- since my father was dead, and all other men-- that we'd be-- that we will be safer in Lwow, which proved to be a illusion.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lwow was just as-- and Lwow was part of Galicia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how-- it was actually-- that's an old name for the Austria-Hungarian monarchy province.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before the World War I, Galicia was part of Austriohungarian monarchy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Poland was dismembered for several centuries, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and many people did speak German in Lwow and Krakow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- we-- we-- I don't know why my mother had about this illusion that we will be safer in Lwow, which proved to be really just a hope.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we-- we lived outside of ghetto for a while, and then we move into ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to move, though my mother tried to get some papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was hard because my-- my younger brother-- I-- I-- I look-- I look very inconspicuous, but my mother and my younger brother, they would attract attention.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
